This is a README file of SALB.
The README file of PVFS2 are renamed to README.PVFS2

This repository contains the source code of PVFS2 with the SALB algorithm.
The source codes and documents in this repository are only used for academic exchanges, not for commercial activities.


To compile PVFS2 with SALB algorithm, you need to install GNU Scientific Library development package. For example, on a Debian distribution, you can use: apt-get install libgsl0-dev 


More documentations is under development.
However, you can find some details of SALB in PVFS2 in our paper:

Bin Dong, Xiuqiao Li, Limin Xiao, Li Ruan, and Binbin Yu. 2010. Self-Acting Load Balancing with Parallel Sub File Migration for Parallel File System. In Proceedings of the 2010 Third International Joint Conference on Computational Science and Optimization - Volume 02 (CSO '10), Vol. 2. IEEE Computer Society, Washington, DC, USA, 317-321. 

Any questions, you can contact Bin Dong at goon83@126.com or Bondg@cse.buaa.edu.cn

